description:
Renowned Saxophonist and LCCM tutor Dave O’Higgins leads his world class quartet in a performance and Q&A session for LCCM students in January 2015.

Saxophone: Dave O’Higgins

Piano: Graham Harvey

Bass: Geoff Gascoyne

Drums: Sebastiaan De Krom

For more information on our full time or short instrument courses, please visit http://www.lccm.org.uk/courses/
